                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-591-18630406 t18630406-591-punishment-45"></join>on the second Count.—Recommended to mercy by the prosecutrix.—Six Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
